{"tid":1251613,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"香港中古教父拉埋台灣電競選手同奶共﹗","createTime":"2019-06-22T15:11:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T15:11:25.000Z","uid":123940,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"54436ac6700ecafbc536b996d7bb789df3fc875c","tid":1251613,"uid":123940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:11:25.000Z","msg":"呢個冚家剷胡耀東，中古毒撚教父，早前奶共奶到走去篤灰 (HA)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mcxHgDj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmcxHgDj.jpg&h=620303eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pLnLYR7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpLnLYR7.jpg&h=137a85e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢昆到SNK畀佢攞個名喺大陸搞比賽，宜家仲拉埋ET (台灣人) 跟佢搵食，自己奶共都未夠，仲要玩埋兩地分化！要拉埋個台灣電競選手自稱「中國選手」﹐著埋中國選手制服。人哋跟你搵食打個機啫，極其量都係賣身，但你要佢連國都賣埋，佢無辜㗎，冚家剷﹗<br />\n(ET&mdash;台灣KOF電競選手，去年贏左一次既時候仲有小英致電道賀)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6V6T7LA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6V6T7LA.jpg&h=cb08c515&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q9ScDSf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq9ScDSf.jpg&h=eaeb0abc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要KOF比賽獎金都要拖人哋 (歐洲嗰邊，好似而家都未畀人)，正人渣！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW，呢個冚家剷連足球小將係RPG都講得出，仲話走去HKUSPACE教電莖歷史，信佢一成，腦袋失明！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QCj206j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQCj206j.jpg&h=296d92f1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/tech/daily/article/20180714/20449309?fbclid=IwAR1IaHx7j_yhLu4R6uzmZWCAU1foLeh6H8cHOIEBIFRJWusH7Q5yaRsBGPQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Ftech%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180714%2F20449309%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1IaHx7j_yhLu4R6uzmZWCAU1foLeh6H8cHOIEBIFRJWusH7Q5yaRsBGPQ&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3tjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=c17685ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Ftech%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180714%2F20449309%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1IaHx7j_yhLu4R6uzmZWCAU1foLeh6H8cHOIEBIFRJWusH7Q5yaRsBGPQ&h=0c36251b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/tech/daily/article/20180714/20449309?fbclid=IwAR1IaHx7j_yhLu4R6uzmZWCAU1foLeh6H8cHOIEBIFRJWusH7Q5yaRsBGPQ</a><br />\n<br />\n唔差在講埋，條友之前搞中古遊戲展，問人左搲右度搵機擺展覽都算，連人哋個名都唔落，自己攞晒威，仲要慰勞宴係AA制，堂堂教父做人做到咁「度」，真係要畀個like佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />﹗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hd68WE0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHd68WE0.jpg&h=caa95c6e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}